<li>"<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nearer,_My_God,_to_Thee" title="Nearer, My God, to Thee">Nearer, My God, to Thee</a>" hymn lyrics (written 1841) by <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sarah_Flower_Adams" class="mw-redirect" title="Sarah Flower Adams">Sarah Flower Adams</a></li>
